1
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:46,480
Si Xingxuan.

2
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,560
I was wrong about you.

3
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:16,520
What is wrong with me?

4
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,520
How could I get angry at Cangyue?

5
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:27,440
Cangyue.

6
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:29,840
Brother.

7
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,360
Brother, you haven't walked the dog

8
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:34,200
with me for days.

9
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,800
Can you

10
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:39,200
play with me today?

11
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:50,000
Are you unhappy, Brother?

12
00:01:52,479 --> 00:01:54,340
Brother, you have wrinkles here.

13
00:01:59,039 --> 00:01:59,880
I made

14
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,160
Sister Cangyue angry.

15
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,720
Can you help me

16
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:07,040
call Sister Cangyue over?

17
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:07,480
Okay?

18
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,600
Why should I go?

19
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:12,760
Girls need to be coaxed.

20
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:15,000
Brother, you are a fool.

21
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,290
Even Pixiu is smarter than you.

22
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,600
First sweep, sweep away the psychos.

23
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,440
Second sweep, sweep away the jinx.

24
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,500
Third sweep, sweep away Si Xingxuan.

25
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,730
Fourth sweep...

26
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:37,440
Boss, why did you give up the comfortable job

27
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:39,040
of serving tea and pouring water,

28
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,640
and insist on sweeping the floor outside?

29
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:43,360
You're going to sweep a hole in the ground.

30
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:46,400
Because I was born to sweep floors.

31
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,079
His Majesty hasn't come out for two days.

32
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:54,340
I wonder what's wrong.

33
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:57,320
Lady Cangyue has been acting weird lately too.

34
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,880
She hasn't gone in to serve tea to His Majesty for days.

35
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:02,000
Could His Majesty be heartbroken?

36
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:10,320
Boss, what's wrong?

37
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,600
Yeah, tell us.

38
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,200
We'll help you figure it out.

39
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,160
Forget it.

40
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,500
You guys should leave.

41
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,200
Go!

42
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,800
I'm so angry my makeup is ruined.

43
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:43,760
Cangyue.

44
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,240
Cangyue.

45
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:48,880
Get lost!

46
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,200
I won't.

47
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,610
You won't leave, right?

48
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,740
If you don't leave, I'll dump you.

49
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:02,240
I won't leave even if you try to get rid of me.

50
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,140
You didn't.

51
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,040
Don't move. Go back.

52
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,480
I'm leaving.

53
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:09,570
I'm really leaving.

54
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:38,900
What are you doing?

55
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,440
Alright.

56
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,680
So annoying.

57
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,840
Just say what you want to say.

58
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:58,840
I'm sorry.

59
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:02,720
Sorry?

60
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,280
What? I have to leave just because you tell me to?

61
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,080
Do I have to forgive you just because you say sorry?
